instruction: Find the most efficient route to get from point A to point B.
input:
Point A: Central Park, New York, NY
Point B: Empire State Building, New York, NY
output: The most efficient route from Central Park to the Empire State Building is to head east on 59th Street. Turn left on Fifth Avenue and continue until you reach 34th Street.
